# PaddleOCR-VL 1.6 weight manifest — re-hosted at xberg-io/paddleocr-vl-1.6, a
# byte-identical mirror of PaddlePaddle/PaddleOCR-VL-1.6 (Apache-2.0). Single source of
# truth: the runtime staging path (model_stager.rs, via include_str!) reads this file.
# Update the model → edit here only.
#
# PaddleOCR-VL 1.6 keeps the same architecture as 1.5 (SigLIP vision encoder + ERNIE
# 4.5 text decoder) and ships weights as a single unsharded model.safetensors file, so
# there is no shard set to enumerate.
